		<section name="Welcome to the Lutece Project ">
            <p>
                Lutece is a portal engine which allows you <strong>to easily create your websites or intranets</strong> 
				based upon HTML, XML... content. 
			</p>
			<p>
			    Lutece provides <strong>a user friendly interface for portal management</strong> and therefore no specific technical skills are required. 
            </p>
            <p>
				This software is implemented in <strong>Java</strong> and based on widely used libraries and frameworks : 
				Spring, Freemarker, Lucene, Ehcache, Jakarta-commons, PDFBox, ... .
				Lutece is <strong>free and Open-Source</strong> : it is distributed under <a href="license.html">a BSD-like license</a>.
            </p>
            <p>
                Languages available are English and French. 
                French users are invited to consult the <a href="http://dev.lutece.paris.fr">french site</a>. 
            </p>
          </section>
		  
